---
title: Mexican Baked Chicken with Seasoned Rice
description: Easy-smothered Mexican chicken is a symphony of flavours for the whole family! Juicy chicken breast can tossed in Mexican Seasoning and topped with a savoury tomato and pepper sauce. All topped with cheese and served over a perfectly fluffy bed of rice!

